== Bambolechea Khursa Mullim Povitr Tritvek Magnnem ==
'''Bambolim Cross - Prayer'''



Deva amchea Bapa, Tuvem monxeachi soddvonn korunk, khursachi 

vatt vinchun kaddli. Tuvem Tujea Putak khursache vollvolle 

ani kollvolle sosunk nirmileam, ani Tannem tuka mog dakhounk 

ani monxachem taronn korunk te tuka omple. Amchea jivitant 

he khuris tum amkam dhaddtai te sosunk ani moniskullache 

soddvonne khatir orpunk, Tuji kurpa amkam di. Mogalla, Jezu, 

Tuka khursar ubhartoch, Tum soglleank Apnnaxim oddun haddttoloi 

mhonn Tunvem bhasavnni keli. Oso Tum hea Bambolechea dongrar 

sogllea jinsacheam monxeank oddun haddtai. Tujea koddvollantlea 

udkan amkam nhannoi, ani rogtan amkam kurpa, ani mog amkam di, 

itlench amkam puro. Povitr Atmea, Jezu Kristan Tuka kalvar dongrar 

Saibinnicher ani Apleam xisancher funklo.  Aiz hea mollar ani 

dongrar sobar dhormanche monis ekvott'tat. Tanchim monan uzvaddai, 

kallzam mogan pettoi, Jezuchem raj vistarai, ani soglleam monxeank 

Tachea rajeant pavoi.



Je upkar ami magtanv te amkam di. 


''Mhoima Bapak ani Putak, ani Povitr Atmeak.''


'''''Amen'''''






